other_tests.findings: Good opacification of the intra- and extra-hepatic biliary ducts, without dilatation, filling defects, or strictures. Mild ductal dilatation of the dorsal duct; findings are consistent with pancreatic divisum, with no communication between the ventral and dorsal ducts.
Mixed bacterial flora (>= 3 colony types), consistent with skin and/or genital contamination.
